<h2>Web Services Credentials</h2>
<p>From the DataShop web application, you can sign up to use web services and retrieve or reset
your web services access credentials. For more information on using web services or to download a
sample client application, see the <a href="http://pslcdatashop.org/about/webservices.html">web services home page</a>.</p>

<h3>Using your access credentials to authenticate</h3>

<p>To authenticate, you need to provide a digital signature, derived from a pair
of public/private access keys, with each request to DataShop web services. The process for creating
this signature is described in the <a href="http://pslcdatashop.org/api/">API reference</a>.</p>

<p>To retrieve or reset your access keys, visit the <a href="WebServicesCredentials">web services credentials page</a>.</p>

